703728f-b.title: Brooklyn: Columbia Street - Baltic Street
703728f-b.text:
Columbia Street, east side, south from and across Baltic Street.
The garage and four-story building,this side of Laltic Street,are
on the N. E. corner.
View 2 shows the N. E. corner buildings, the garage extending
also on Baltic Street(right).
October 15, 1940
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
